    "The most recent multi-modal GenAI systems exacerbate the demand further by requiring large amounts of data for each modality.There is no single organization, even nation, that contains the full data used for training a given LLM.",
    "Data repositories are not monolithic data containers but a list of labels and data links to other servers that actually contain the corresponding data samples.",
